  on february 21 , 2010 , two days before the beginning of ladies ' figure skating competition at the winter olympics in vancouver , her mother , thérèse rochette , died of a heart attack at age 55 at vancouver general hospital after arriving to watch her compete ; rochette chose to remain in the competition and skate in her mother 's honour .

women in sports : in the 2010 olympics joannie rochette managed a bronze in this sport just days after the death of her mother

